name: Remote Party
description:
Remote Party, is a collection of 3 video-loops inspired by people who partied alone from home, through internet, during the pandemic. 

Are you up for a bit of dance today? You could also try this with any type of Cumbia, Merengue, Salsa, Rumba. And many other latin rhythms. Enjoy!

The original music done by Cristian Marcico
